short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows the Rate My Professors rating of RIT professors while searching for classes on Tiger Center and CSH Schedule Maker.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Professors' names will now link to their Rate My Professors page (or the search results if not found).

To better find professors, this extension will try different first/middle name combos as well as associated nicknames and diminutive names.

The Github repo is here: https://github.com/CalvinWu4/RIT-Rate-My-Professors-Extension
